OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHostile states are         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftargeting you, Speaker     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwarns MPs                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs have been warned they are being    
OL,6, targeted by "hostile states", with     
OL,7, their mobile phones "a potential       
OL,8, goldmine" of sensitive information.    
OL,10,FIn a letter to MPs, Commons Speaker Sir
OL,11,FLindsay Hoyle urged MPs to avoid using 
OL,12,Ftheir phone for sensitive conversations
OL,13,For even having it in the same room.    
OL,15,F"If hackers have switched on the       
OL,16,Fmicrophone on one phone everyone in the
OL,17,Froom might be overheard," he wrote.    
OL,19,FThe government is creating a taskforce 
OL,20,Fto defend the UK from hostile actors.  
